     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="11"/>
   <head>To the Authour.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <seg rend="decorInit">D</seg>Emereits <hi>Maro</hi> from proud <hi>Mars</hi> his throne</l>
      <l>A freindlie look, or yit a thankfull sho?</l>
      <l>Deserueth <hi>Naso</hi> from young <hi>Venus</hi> sone</l>
      <l>A cheirfull smyll? (if they can haue no mo)</l>
      <l>Yes faith: I pray then what should be thy hyre?</l>
      <l>Who maks all men thir monarch gods admyre.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Has not thy Pen proclaim'd att lairge to all,</l>
      <l>Sterne <hi>Mars</hi> his soldier great <hi>Penardo</hi> strong?</l>
      <l>Has not thy layes learn'd how <hi>Laissa's</hi> thrall</l>
      <l>To craftie loues allurments too too long?</l>
      <l>Then both the warreou<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>s, &amp; the wanton's theam<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>
      </l>
      <l>Should spare no pains, to aeterneize thy name,</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>William. Tod.</signed>
   </closer>
